  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Master the art of stealth in Super Silent Sensei, a fast-paced, casual stealth game where precision and cunning are key. Step into the role of a legendary ninja on a mission to rescue elusive aliens scattered across the military compound Zone 52 without ever being captured.</i></strong><br><strong><i></i></strong><br><strong><i>Stay hidden, stay silent, and use your environment to outsmart patrolling enemies and traps, you only have one </i></strong><br><strong><i></i></strong><br><u><strong><i>Get all aliens and make a run for the escape point!</i></strong></u><strong><i></i></strong><br><strong><i></i></strong><br><strong><i>Only the most disciplined Sensei will succeed.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/05d527fa4fdb87cf977747fc2451e82a.poster.avif?t=1755600764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/05d527fa4fdb87cf977747fc2451e82a.webm?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/05d527fa4fdb87cf977747fc2451e82a.mp4?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/5cff4b5c4b078c9c662111d3bb2df84c.poster.avif?t=1755600764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/5cff4b5c4b078c9c662111d3bb2df84c.webm?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/5cff4b5c4b078c9c662111d3bb2df84c.mp4?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/2f1326df7b3a13916f3136186d830526.poster.avif?t=1755600764\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/2f1326df7b3a13916f3136186d830526.webm?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/2f1326df7b3a13916f3136186d830526.mp4?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong> </strong></i><br><i><strong>Do you have the patience, skill, and precision to remain unseen? Step into the shadows and prove yourself as the Super Silent Sensei.  </strong></i><br><i><strong>  </strong></i><br><i><strong>  </strong></i><br><i><strong>THANK YOU FOR YOUR SUPPORT!</strong></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.poster.avif?t=1755600764\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.webm?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381650/extras/cded50009e230e8d156bc23955dbd7b1.mp4?t=1755600764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
